肤医学与美容生技，全系列产品通过低敏、安定性临床测试，全方位解决肌肤问题。</p-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mpmp\">\r\n<h2>与台湾医院院系技术交流。</h2>\r\n<!--h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #292929;\">√ 以最安全有效的成分 造就最完美无瑕的肌肤</h3-->\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/02.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/sss.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mpmp\">\r\n<h2>与台湾大叶大学合作，成立森田研究所。</h2>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/06.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/07.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/08.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/09.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mpmp\">\r\n<h2>专注研发</h2>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; float: left; margin-right: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/新增获奖记录8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','研发理念','','publish','closed','closed','','philosophy','','','2016-04-13 17:17:12','2016-04-13 09:17:12','',5,'http://www.drmorita.cc/?page_id=9',1,'page','',0),(10,1,'2014-11-19 13:44:22','2014-11-19 05:44:22','','研发理念','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-v1','','','2014-11-19 13:44:22','2014-11-19 05:4