  </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"overflow:hidden;padding-top:35px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"width:218px;float:left;margin-right:25px;\">\r\n                <img style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"http://www.drmorita.cc/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"“我要上学”大型主题公益系列活动\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"float:left;width:639px;\">\r\n                <h2 style=\"width:100%;font-size:24px;color:black;margin-top:0px;padding-bottom:10px;border-bottom:#e5e5e5 solid 1px;\">“我要上学”大型主题公益系列活动</h2>\r\n                <p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#868686;line-height:25px;\">\r\n                自2003年起至今，“MusicRadio我要上学”大型主题公益系列活动是由中央人民广播电台MusicRadio音乐之声与中国儿童少年基金会共同主办,以帮助贫困地区孩子上学为目的的公益项目。<br>\r\n                2012年，森田首席科研医师周俊旭先生担任了“我要上学”大型主题公益系列活动的爱心大使。2014年，森田大陆总经理林盟钦先生担任了“我要上学”大型主题公益系列活动的爱心守望者。\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>','社会责任','','publish','closed','closed','','responsibility','','','2015-01-20 11:12:35','2015-01-20 03:12:35','',29,'http://www.drmorita.cc/?page_id=25',2,'page','',0),(26,1,'2014-11-19 13:53:27','2014-11-19 05:53:27','','社会责任','','inherit','open','open','','25-revision-v1','','','2014-11-19 13:53:27','2014-11-19 05:53:27','',25,'http://www.drmorita.cc/uncategorized/20141119_26.html',0,'revision','',0),(27,1,'2014-11-19 13:54:22','2014-11-19 05:54:22','','研发中心','','publish','closed','closed','','center','','','2016-04-06 16:28:48','2016-04-06 08:28:48','',0,'http://www.drmorita.cc/?page_id=27',0,'page','',0),(28,1,'2014-11-19 13:54:22','2014-11-19 05:54:22','','研发中心','','inherit','open','open','','27-revision-v1','','','2014-11-19 13:54:22','2014-11-19 05:54:22','',27,'http://www.drmorita.cc/uncategorized/20141119_28.html',0,'revision','',0),(29,1,'2014-11-19 13:56:45','2014-11-19 05:56:45','','走进森田','','publish','closed','closed','','closeto','','','2014-11-19 13:56:45','2014-11-19 05:56:45','',0,'http://www.drmorita.cc/?page_id=29',1,'page','',0),(30,1,'201